{
  "stem": "58.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They never came back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And I-- then he took me down.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He said-- he told the people to go into camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He asked me why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I say, when I come to work, I have the-- the occasion-- I have hot water and I have a powder that we use to clean the things in the-- [INAUDIBLE] dry.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And whenever I come in, I wash my clothes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I work night shift.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In the morning, it dries out at the oven.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It's so hot.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That's why.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I say-- I say, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They haven't got the same situation I have.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But still, he says, they could keep a little bit cleaner.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There's-- there is water in the camp here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They could wash.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Some-- some neglected themselves.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was the worst thing, if you went down with cleanliness.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They hate it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Anyway, after this I worked for-- in [INAUDIBLE] for a long time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 9 SECONDS] and until we had to-- the Russians came 10 kilometers from this factory.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they said, it came on order, it's like a tornado hit them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "To pack everything, pack the machines.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We are moving out to [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Czechow ?].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Czechow? ?] How far would it take the Russians to come to [?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Czechow? ?] But they tried.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They didn't believe that the end is coming.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "OK, we packed everything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We packed in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And then the Russians came closer, they said [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "They put us in trains and they shipped us out to [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Czechow. ?] [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We came to [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Czechow. ?] There's an empty-- empty-- empty lofts.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Nowhere to sleep.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "They put some straw on the cement, where we sleep.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "There were three places in [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Czechow ?] from the same factory, ammunition factory.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
